                },
                {
                    "insert": "\n2. "
                },
                {
                    "attributes": {
                        "bold": true
                    },
                    "insert": "Stable Server Components"
                },
                {
                    "attributes": {
                        "header": 3
                    },
                    "insert": "\n"
                },
                {
                    "insert": "After years of experimentation and community feedback, "
                },
                {
                    "attributes": {
                        "bold": true
                    },
                    "insert": "Server Components"
                },
                {
                    "insert": " are now officially stable in this release. Server Components allow developers to render parts of their application on the server, reducing the amount of JavaScript sent to the client and improving performance.\nThis feature is particularly useful for data-heavy applications, as it enables seamless data fetching and rendering on the server without sacrificing interactivity on the client.\n"
                },
                {
                    "attributes": {
                        "bold": true
                    },
                    "insert": "Key Benefits:"
                },
                {
                    "insert": "\nReduced bundle size"
                },
                {
                    "attributes": {
                        "list": "bullet"
                    },
                    "insert": "\n"
                },
                {
                    "insert": "Faster page loads"
                },
