                    "insert": "The latest React release is packed with features that make building modern web applications faster, easier, and more efficient. From the revolutionary React Compiler to stable Server Components and enhanced hooks, there’s something for everyone in this update.\nAs always, the React team has provided extensive documentation and migration guides to help you make the most of these new features. Whether you're starting a new project or upgrading an existing one, now is the perfect time to explore what React has to offer in 2025.\n"
